      </div>
      <div class="jumbotron">
         <h1>{{ _("Electronic payments for a liberal society!") }}</h1>
	 <p>{{ _("Taler is a new electronic payment system under development
	    at <a href='http://www.inria.fr/'>Inria</a>.  Today, this website only
