	     never learn how you spent your electronic money. However, you can
	     prove that you paid in court if necessary.") }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <h2>{{ _("Libre") }}</h2>
	  <p>{{ _("Taler is free software from <a href='http://www.gnu.org/'>GNU</a> implementing an open protocol.
